The paper discusses the use of AI learning-based model predictive control algorithms for tissue manipulation via a surgical robotic system. This involves vision strategies and the use of reinforcement learning and learning from demonstration algorithms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
